  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large pot, sauté the caramelized onion, carrots, celery, and garlic in a little olive oil until tender.",
    "2. Add the vegetable broth, cannellini beans, and chopped kale.",
    "3. Bring to a boil, then reduce the heat and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "4. Stir in the cubed bread and cook until the bread is softened.",
    "5. Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "6. Serve hot, topped with chopped ribollita and a drizzle of olive oil if desired."
